title: BE YOUR BEST
itunes:title: BE YOUR BEST
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
Dedicate Yourself To Becoming Your Best Self!! The goal is not be be better than others, but your previous self. You don't need to be perfect but you are confined by the walls you build. The secret to your success is found within you. One of the most inspiring Motivational Speech Compilations Ever! Special thanks to the speaker, Pete Cohen (https://bit.ly/PeteCohenMotiversity), and the composers from Cloud181 music (https://www.cloud181.com), Jemma Murray and Samuel John!


Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic), Audiomachine (https://www.youtube.com/audiomachine), and Audiojungle (https://audiojungle.net/).




Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
